<section class="guideSection">
  <h2>Why Newspaper Pots Work for Seedlings</h2>

  <p>
    Seedlings are sensitive to root disturbance. Traditional containers require removing the plant, which can stress roots.
  </p>

  <p>
    Newspaper pots allow you to:
  </p>

  <ul class="plainList">
    <li>plant directly into soil</li>
    <li>avoid transplant shock</li>
    <li>reduce plastic use</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    The paper breaks down as roots expand.
  </p>
</section>

